{"tid":1838690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上海迪士尼樂園明起關閉","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T06:23:53.000Z","uid":152476,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2d77cd6ff54b696e3561f19cfef44dfb350eb99a","tid":1838690,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案持續增加，陸續有城市宣布取消農曆新年期間的慶祝活動，或者關閉旅遊景點。<br />\n<br />\n上海迪士尼樂園宣布，明日起暫時關閉迪士尼樂園、迪士尼小鎮和星願公園，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n福建廈門鼓浪嶼，山西平遙古城、江蘇南京玄武湖、浙江杭州西湖及廣東廣州塔等多地景點，今日起暫時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504620-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504620-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=adac2879\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504620-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d1b47313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504620-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"39ff70278fe25d096fe8324bf8989548ed7dd16d","tid":1838690,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"香港政府：歡迎黎香港"},{"pid":"37f5e29ca48f96b0a27e1ed0fa418e05879dbcd3","tid":1838690,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ff70278fe25d096fe8324bf8989548ed7dd16d","tid":1838690,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"香港政府：歡迎黎香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d984579474fbd2adf957e57a21ca086529ced